1.1.20100407
============
* Cédric Dufour <cedric.dufour@ced-network.net>
  - Fixed RSS version format in XML output
  - Improved RSS compliance to RSS 2.0 standard
  - Added 'HTTP_X_FORWARDED_FOR' server variable while checking authentication IP filter

1.1.20100311
============
* Cédric Dufour <cedric.dufour@ced-network.net>
  - Added dependencies file
  - Fixed uninitialized parameters array in global environment initialization

1.1.20100203
============
* Cédric Dufour <cedric.dufour@ced-network.net>
  - GIT versioning
  - Fixed empty string bug in PHP_APE_Type_Email
  - Added external customization possibility for PHP_APE_ROOT constant

1.1.20091203
============
* Cédric Dufour <cedric.dufour@ced-network.net>
  - Improved HTML authentication components to allow cross HTTP/HTTPS/hostnames authentication
    NOTE: make sure to set the 'session.cookie_domain' PHP parameter to the proper domain to
          allow cross hostnames authentication

1.1.20091124
============
* Cédric Dufour <cedric.dufour@ced-network.net>
  - Fixed 'Date/Time' types parsing bug (introduced by 'Numeric' parsing in previous version)

1.1.20091123
============
* Cédric Dufour <cedric.dufour@ced-network.net>
  - Added (successful) authentication logging
  - Added 'Numeric' format preference ('php_ape.data.format.numeric') and parsing resiliency

1.1.20090826
============
* Cédric Dufour <cedric.dufour@ced-network.net>
  - Fixed authentication and preferences URL bug
  - Removed user-customizable HTML factory/controller from generic workspace

1.1.20090825
============
* Cédric Dufour <cedric.dufour@ced-network.net>
  - Fixed authentication heartbeat (which was not rightfully saved in session)
  - Added 'print' icon in CSS stylesheets
  - Modified authentication template for leaner aspect
  - Improved HTML data views for better flexibility
  - Improved HTML data JavaScript for better scalability
  - Added default resource localization parameter ('php_ape.localize.resource')
    WARNING: defaults to 'false'; set to 'true' for localized applications
  - Added configurable resource identifier computation parameter ('php_ape.html.rid')
    WARNING: defaults to 'short'; set to 'md5' for legacy compatibility

1.0.20090707
============
* Cédric Dufour <cedric.dufour@ced-network.net>
  - Fixed the cache signature used to cache configuration parameters in 'Environment.php'
  - Fixed JavaScript bug which prevented GET forms to be submitted
  - Fixed CSS stylesheets to include "@media print" directives
  - Fixed array-based resultset filtering to handle non-ASCII strings
  - Removed print-specific CSS stylesheets
  - Removed the login button in the default HTML controller
  - Added 'DarkTango' CSS stylesheet
  - Added back label/button HTML component
  - Added preferences redirection target
  - Added position data in file/image resultsets (allowing previous/next browsing)

1.0.20080827
